OL,3,CPassengers left stranded on Greek
OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,FPassengers flying from a Greek island
OL,7,Fare desperate to return home after
OL,8,Fbecoming stranded for more than 50
OL,9,Fhours due to a worldwide IT outage.
OL,11,FHolidaymakers were left stranded in
OL,12,FCorfu after the outage, which affected
OL,13,FMicrosoft Windows PCs around the
OL,14,Fworld, was triggered by a bug in an
OL,15,Fupdate rolled out by the cybersecurity
OL,16,Ffirm CrowdStrike on Friday 19 July.
