OL,3,CPassengers left stranded on Greek
OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,FThe Manchester-bound passengers were
OL,7,Fjust some of the thousands who
OL,8,Freceived numerous emails about sudden
OL,9,Fflight cancellations after the outage
OL,10,Fcaused several issues including
OL,11,Ffailure of online check-ins and blank
OL,12,Fdeparture screens, with several
OL,13,Fairports forced to do check-in and
OL,14,Fboarding manually.
OL,16,FThis led to a build-up of delayed
OL,17,Fflights and cancellations causing
OL,18,F"chaos" and "horrendous queues".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
