OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,FOne passenger, who had travelled to
OL,7,FCorfu with their mum, described the
OL,8,F"nightmare" they are currently facing.
OL,10,FThe passenger, who asked to remain
OL,11,Fanonymous said: "Our flight was due to
OL,12,Ffly at 2:20pm on Friday back to
OL,13,FManchester.
OL,15,F"They picked us up from the hotel and
OL,16,Fwhen we got to the airport, there were
OL,17,Fhuge queues, it was chaos.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
