OL,3,CPassengers left stranded on Greek
OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,F"It was horrendous, there were people
OL,7,Feverywhere. Some had to stand outside
OL,8,Fin 35C heat because the airport was so
OL,9,Fbusy.
OL,11,F"Everyone was queuing because the
OL,12,Fflights were all delayed."
OL,14,FThe passenger claimed that from 4pm on
OL,15,FSunday 21 July, they were still
OL,16,Fsitting in the departures lounge and
OL,17,Fleft completely in the dark about when
OL,18,Ftheir rescheduled flight would depart.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
