OL,6,FThey also say they were told to book
OL,7,Ftheir own hotels for two nights after
OL,8,Ftheir initial TOM2519 flight was
OL,9,Fcancelled on Friday, but 50 hours
OL,10,Flater they were still waiting to hear
OL,11,Fwhether the plane will even leave the
OL,12,Frunway.
OL,14,FThey claimed that some passengers, who
OL,15,Fcouldn't afford another last minute
OL,16,Fexpense of booking accommodation, have
OL,17,Fspent two gruelling nights sleeping in
OL,18,Fthe airport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
