OL,6,FThe passenger flying with Tui added:
OL,7,F"They told us about the IT issues and
OL,8,Fthat it was a global issue, so we
OL,9,Fstayed on the transfer coach for three
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,F"We finally got into the airport and
OL,13,Fthere was a lot of waiting around -
OL,14,Fbut our flight still wasn't on the
OL,15,Fdepartures board.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
