OL,3,CPassengers left stranded on Greek
OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,F"Eventually we got an email saying the
OL,7,Fflight was cancelled completely and
OL,8,Fthat accommodation was being arranged,
OL,9,Fbut when we got to the Tui desk, they
OL,10,Ftold us they couldn't find us a hotel
OL,11,Fbecause there were so many guests and
OL,12,Fthe island was at capacity, and that
OL,13,Fwe had to sort it ourselves.
OL,15,F"We booked a package holiday and this
OL,16,Fshould've been sorted. All these
OL,17,Fpassengers were on booking.com finding
OL,18,Frandom rooms and hotels where we could
OL,19,Fwith our own money.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
