OL,6,F"A few young girls that had no savings
OL,7,For money in the bank to book somewhere
OL,8,Fhad to sleep in the airport."
OL,10,FAlong with her mum, the pair were
OL,11,Flucky enough to secure a hotel for
OL,12,FFriday night, believing they would be
OL,13,Fon the next flight home the following
OL,14,Fday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
