OL,6,FHowever, passengers later received
OL,7,Fanother email,from Tui, saying that
OL,8,Fdue to being 'severely impacted' by
OL,9,Fthe global IT issue, the airline was
OL,10,F'not able to operate a flight back to
OL,11,Fthe UK' due to the 'scale of
OL,12,Fdisruption' on Saturday 20 July.
OL,14,FThe email said: "We absolutely
OL,15,Funderstand this is not the end of your
OL,16,Fholiday you would expect and apologise
OL,17,Fagain for the impact this has had."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
