OL,3,CPassengers left stranded on Greek
OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,FA number of passengers were once again
OL,7,Fforced to book other hotels at their
OL,8,Fown expense. The airline has said that
OL,9,Fthey will 'reimburse reasonable costs'
OL,10,Fincurred by passengers.
OL,12,FOn Saturday evening, passengers hoping
OL,13,Fto get back to Manchester then
OL,14,Freceived a further email from Tui,
OL,15,Fwith the airline informing them that
OL,16,Fthey were 'finalising details' and
OL,17,Fwould provide an update later that
OL,18,Fevening on their plans to fly them
OL,19,Fhome.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
