OL,4,Cisland after global IT outage
OL,6,FOn Sunday at 3am, a further message
OL,7,Fwas received, confirming that the
OL,8,Festimated departure time out of Corfu
OL,9,Fwould be at 12pm later that day. The
OL,10,Fflight had then been rescheduled again
OL,11,Ffor 5.25pm from Corfu - 51 hours late.
OL,13,FThe woman said: "The emails have been
OL,14,Fterrible. We came today to check in at
OL,15,F9am, then at 11.30am we are told it
OL,16,Fwas delayed again. It has been 50
OL,17,Fhours now and we still don't know
OL,18,Fwhat's happening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
