OL,6,F"Everyone is just miserable and angry.
OL,7,FIt's been a nightmare. People have
OL,8,Fwork tomorrow. My mum works for the
OL,9,FNHS and was like: 'What am I going to
OL,10,Fdo?'. People will be losing a day in
OL,11,Fwork and have commitments, will they
OL,12,Fpay our wages?"
OL,14,FA statement shared by Tui on social
OL,15,Fmedia said: "Following the global IT
OL,16,Fissue impacting businesses around the
OL,17,Fworld, we would like to apologise to
OL,18,Feveryone affected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
