OL,6,F"Whilst the original IT issue was
OL,7,Foutside of our control, the impact to
OL,8,Four systems has meant that our flight
OL,9,Fprogramming continues to suffer delays
OL,10,Fand cancellations.
OL,12,F"We are very sorry to all those
OL,13,Fcustomers impacted as we understand
OL,14,Fhow disappointing this is. We ask that
OL,15,Fall TUI customers due to travel this
OL,16,Fweekend regularly check the Travel
OL,17,FInformation page of the TUI website
OL,18,Ffor the latest updates. Your TUI Team."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
