OL,6,FThe airline has also apologised as it
OL,7,Fannounced that it has had to cancel
OL,8,Fseveral flights from Manchester
OL,9,FAirport on Sunday as it continues to
OL,10,Ffeel the effects of the outage.
OL,12,FIn a statement on its website, Tui
OL,13,Fsaid: "Due to the global IT issue at
OL,14,Fairports and airlines around the world
OL,15,Fon Friday, TUI's overall service this
OL,16,Fweekend was heavily impacted and we
OL,17,Fwould like to apologise to everyone
OL,18,Faffected.
