OL,6,F"If you are due to travel with us
OL,7,Ftoday, we ask for your patience and
OL,8,Funderstanding. Customers should travel
OL,9,Fto the airport as normal unless you
OL,10,Fare contacted by TUI or your non-TUI
OL,11,Fairline directly. However, please plan
OL,12,Fahead and expect longer waiting times."
OL,14,FThe airline said those on cancelled
OL,15,Fflights have several options depending
OL,16,Fon whether their booking is flight-
OL,17,Fonly or a package holiday, adding that
OL,18,Fimpacted customers will be contacted
OL,19,Fdirectly.
