OL,6,FIt said: "Customers who no longer wish
OL,7,Fto travel can cancel and receive a
OL,8,Ffull refund of the holiday cost. They
OL,9,Fwill also receive a #200 per adult and
OL,10,F#100 per child TUI holiday voucher off
OL,11,Fa future holiday.
OL,13,F"Refunds will be processed within 14
OL,14,Fdays. For customers who have booked
OL,15,Fjust a flight with us, as this flight
OL,16,Fis cancelled you will automatically
OL,17,Freceive a full refund within 14 days."
